        "text": "9 September 1948\nIN REPLY ADDRESS BOTH\nCOMMUNICATION AND EN-\nVELOPE TO COMMANDING\nGENERAL, AIR MATERIEL\nCOMMAND, ATTENTION\nFOLLOWING OFFICE SYMBOL:\nMCLAXD-3\n3P-CO\nL-32\nDirector\nFederal Bureau of Investigation\nDepartment of Justice\nWashington, D. C.\nATTN: FBI Laboratory"
      },
